title: Bitcoin whales send BTC price under $109.5K as market ‘wobbles’ into US PCE
summary: Crypto traders are noticing familiar patterns in Bitcoin whale behavior this week, just in time for the release of US inflation data. Keep an eye on the market

![ Bitcoin whales send BTC price under $109.5K as market ‘wobbles’ into US PCE ](https://images.cointelegraph.com/images/528_aHR0cHM6Ly9zMy5jb2ludGVsZWdyYXBoLmNvbS91cGxvYWRzLzIwMjQtMTIvMDE5MzhlZjUtOTA2Yi03ZmI1LTgwYjktNTk1NzNmZjJiY2Mw.jpg)

Crypto traders are noticing familiar patterns in Bitcoin whale behavior this week, just in time for the release of US inflation data. Keep an eye on the market as these "spoofy" trends unfold.
